ActCanada Customs and Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of CONNIE IDA ROVETO of Toronto, Ontario, to be Chair of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Michael L. Turcotte, whose term has expired.
